{
  "stem": "10.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "elapsed_s": 57.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The SS man, this Neubert, he had the job to register the people who were selected to go to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he had the names and the numbers on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when we saw between the 120 they selected, we saw some young people, I went again to him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, Neubert, there are two or three I would like to save.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This is my friend's son.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Or, he is from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Naturally, he knew I'm lying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But he crossed out two or three.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He couldn't cross out 120 because he had to deliver the people the doctor selected.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So, again, we saved a couple three.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But now the trucks arrived to take those sick people, the 120 or so, to Auschwitz, to Birkenau, to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were so sick already, they couldn't even get up on the truck.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we were helping them to go on the truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you know-- it took me years after the liberation, I was fighting with my conscience, I am actually part-- I'm guilty.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I let them-- I helped them going to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But later on, naturally, I understood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, I helped them to make it easier, the few last couple hours or something, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And those people who were already on the truck, they were very sick, even without mind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their minds didn't work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they still had the strength to take off jacket or the shoes, throw it over the truck, leave it for the other ones who are alive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, this is part of the resistance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe there were exceptions, you know, some little town or something that depicted a Jew or something, but I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they had the largest anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was in the hospital working about three months, maybe less.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two months.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden I was assigned to the re-educational camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This meant-- re-educational camp consisted of prisoners of non-Jews who worked for the Germans during the war as [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] forced laborers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were brought from all occupied countries to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they worked for them in the factory which we had to build-- this Buna Werke.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they went on [GERMAN], when they extended the [GERMAN]-- they came late, or they run away from work, or they committed sabotage, this was [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] the biggest crime they committed.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were brought to this camp depending on the crimes they committed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The least was in months, the worst, for six months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE], this re-education camp, actually translated is-- re-educational camp is [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[GERMAN] means education.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So everybody thinks it's a school, and you teach them history or languages or something, mathematic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were taken to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had to march with all other prisoners, who were there forever, to work at the factory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they were separated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the separated, they were same thing in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In this big Buna camp, in front at the gate, there were five barracks separated by an additional fence.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they put me in charge of.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "From the beginning, my camp oldest in the hospital was a Polish doctor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he appointed me to go there to establish an ambulance and take care of the people who come into this camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Not in order to bring some of the sick to the main hospital, to us, but I should treat them there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was about a week-- and there was already a camp oldest, a half Jew, a German, a half Jew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I started to talk with him-- I had my job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I established an ambulance, and when people were sick, I treated them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When they got very sick, you know, seriously sick, I took them to the hospital, doctors and everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a week passed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the camp oldest-- I was sleeping with him together in one room-- tells me, Sieg, I'm going to run away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going to escape.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, would you join me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't tell him yes or no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was thinking about it, if to join him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came to the decision not to, because I told myself, when I escape, and I probably would be able-- I would be lucky enough to escape because of my languages.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I speak German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he is a German, speaks only German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I thought myself, OK, I will be lucky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I get out, I'm in hiding somewhere, and I can maybe survive the war to the end.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we knew already what's going on the front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans had to retreat since Stalingrad, and the western front wasn't too rosy either.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
